name: The World's End Entertainment
description:
In a world of ever-changing events, try to find a balance in this cold war enviroment.

Features

  • Prevent a post-apocalyptic future through your decisions.
  • Try to stay sane while nuclear fallout is just two minutes away.
  • Quality cold war aesthetic and lively SFX to accompany you through existential dread.

Credits

Ali Eser
Gokcen Karaagac
Yarkin Deniz Cetin

Made in 26 hours during TaleWorlds Game Jam II
